Hey tbl_ood,

You’re all set up–welcome to your new WeTransfer account. Now it’s (even) easier to get your files where they need to be.

Keep ideas moving

With a WeTransfer account you don’t have to worry about verifying your email whenever you send a file. Just drag and drop to share your big ideas via a link or email.

 <https://email.wetransfer.net/emails/onboarding/keep_ideas_moving.png> 	
Totally secure

All information is fully encrypted, with malware scanning, secure transfers via TLS, and safe storage with AES-256. So you and your transfers are always covered.

 <https://email.wetransfer.net/emails/onboarding/totally_secure.png> 	
Let's go → <https://wetransfer.com/transfers?trk=TRN_FR_ONB_01&utm_campaign=TRN_FR_ONB_01&utm_medium=email&utm_source=sendgrid>
